---
<BaseLayout
  title="PVC 电线电缆料产品目录"
  description="PVC 电线电缆料详细规格型产品目录：70℃ 绝缘料、护套料、电子料、插头料、105℃ 耐高温料、-40℃ 耐寒料、高透明料、雾面料、改性橡塑料。每类产品的用途、适合客户、加工方式、典型规格、询价要点。"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: '首页', href: '/' },
    { name: '产品目录', href: '/products/' },
  ]}
  jsonLd={{
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'ItemList',
    name: '湘发顺 PVC 电线电缆料产品目录',
    itemListElement: products.map((p, i) => ({
      '@type': 'ListItem',
      position: i + 1,
      item: {
        '@type': 'Product',
        name: p.name,
        category: p.category,
        description: p.summary,
        url: `https://xfspvc.com/products/#${p.id}`,
        brand: { '@type': 'Brand', name: '湘发顺 (Xiangfa Shun)' },
        manufacturer: { '@type': 'Organization', name: '佛山市三水湘发顺塑料有限公司' },
        offers: {
          '@type': 'Offer',
          availability: 'https://schema.org/MadeToOrder',
          priceCurrency: 'CNY',
          seller: { '@type': 'Organization', name: '佛山市三水湘发顺塑料有限公司' },
        },
      },
    })),
  }}
>
  <!-- 页头 -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">首页</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
        <span>产品目录</span>
      </nav>
      <div class="section-eyebrow page-eyebrow">CATALOG · 9 CATEGORIES</div>
      <h1>PVC 电线电缆料 · 产品目录</h1>
      <p class="page-header-sub">
        以下为常规品类的典型规格范围。具体配方、颜色、性能以双方沟通确认的技术单为准。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 目录导航 -->
  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cat-nav">
        <span class="cat-nav-title">快速跳转：</span>
        {products.map((p) => (
          <a href={`#${p.id}`} class="cat-nav-link">{p.icon} {p.name}</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 产品列表 -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="catalog-layout">
        <aside class="catalog-sidebar" aria-label="产品目录">
          <div class="catalog-sidebar-inner">
            <div class="catalog-sidebar-title">产品目录</div>
            <nav class="catalog-toc">
              {products.map((p, i) => (
                <a href={`#${p.id}`} class={i === 0 ? 'is-active' : ''} data-toc-link={p.id}>
                  <span class="toc-no">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
                  <span class="toc-text">
                    <strong>{p.name}</strong>
                    <small>{p.category}</small>
                  </span>
                </a>
              ))}
            </nav>
            <a href="/tools/inquiry/" class="catalog-sidebar-cta">提交询盘</a>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <div class="catalog-content">
      {products.map((p, i) => (
        <ProductDetail
          id={p.id}
          name={p.name}
          category={p.category}
          summary={p.summary}
          useCases={p.useCases}
          suitableCustomers={p.suitableCustomers}
          processing={p.processing}
          specs={p.specs}
          concerns={p.concerns}
          inquiryNeeds={p.inquiryNeeds}
          index={i}
        />
      ))}

      <!-- 询价入口 -->
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-box catalog-cta">
        <div class="catalog-cta-text">
          <h3>没有找到完全匹配的产品？</h3>
          <p>可以按客户要求开发配方、做小批量试样。请直接电话或微信沟通。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="catalog-cta-actions">
          <a href={`tel:${phoneNumber}`} class="btn btn-phone btn-lg">📞 {phoneNumber}</a>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">查看联系方式</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const tocLinks = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll<HTMLAnchorElement>('[data-toc-link]'));
  const sections = tocLinks
    .map((link) => {
      const id = link.dataset.tocLink;
      const section = id ? document.getElementById(id) : null;
      return section ? { id, section } : null;
    })
    .filter(Boolean) as Array<{ id: string; section: HTMLElement }>;

  const setActive = (id: string) => {
    tocLinks.forEach((link) => {
      link.classList.toggle('is-active', link.dataset.tocLink === id);
    });
  };

  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
    (entries) => {
      const visible = entries
        .filter((entry) => entry.isIntersecting)
        .sort((a, b) => b.intersectionRatio - a.intersectionRatio)[0];
      if (visible?.target?.id) setActive(visible.target.id);
    },
    {
      rootMargin: '-24% 0px -58% 0px',
      threshold: [0.08, 0.18, 0.32, 0.5],
    }
  );

  sections.forEach(({ section }) => observer.observe(section));
</script>

